parameters.name: Year
parameters.description:
Quantity:  Year of the observation
              Unit: Integer years

parameters.name: DOY
parameters.description:
Quantity: Day of year of the observation, days
              are counted from 1 on
              Unit: Integer days

parameters.name: Hour
parameters.description:
Quantity:  Hour of the observation
              Unit: Integer hours

parameters.name: Min
parameters.description:
Quantity:  Minute of the observation
              Unit: Integer minutes

parameters.name: Sec
parameters.description:
Quantity:  Second of the observation
              Unit: Decimal seconds

parameters.name: Decyear
parameters.description:
Quantity: Fractional year of the observation. Includes the
              full time information in one number. When converting
              to day of year, ensure that round years
              (like 1995.00) have to be equal to DOY
              1, not DOY 0.
              Unit: Decimal years

parameters.name: Step
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              For HGA_Flag=1, "step" shows the actual motor positions
              0-7. For HGA_Flag=0 this information is not available
              and the value set to invalid (-1E38).
              Unit: Integer dimensionless number

parameters.name: Spin
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              For HGA_Flag=1, "spin" is the number of sectors
              in the sky. Its range is 0-63. For
              HGA_Flag=0, this information is not available and the
              value set to invalid (-1E38).
              Unit: Integer dimensionless number

parameters.name: Energy_keV
parameters.description:
Quantity: Deposited energy in CMS/TOFxE solid state detector
              KT. This energy is lower than the ambient
              energy of the particle due to the pulse
              height defect and because the energy was reduced
              when the particle passed the START foil and
              detector dead layer.
              Unit: keV

parameters.name: TOF_ns
parameters.description:
Quantity: Ion time of flight within the CMS/TOFxE
              instrument between the START foil and the KT
              detector. Can be used in combination with the
              deposited energy to identify the ion species. Note
              that the ion in the instrument is slower
              than in ambient space because it lost energy
              when passing the START foil.
              Unit: nanoseconds

parameters.name: etcode
parameters.description:
Quantity:  This is technical information added for completeness.
              Unit: Integer dimensionless number

parameters.name: detector
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              It lists the CMS subsystem: 0 for TOFxE
              end, 1 for Jb/Kb and 3 for Ja/Kb
              of the two DeltaExE ends.
              Unit: Integer dimensionless number

parameters.name: hga_flag
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              Is 1 if the data originates from record
              mode, 0 if the data is from real
              time mode.
              Unit: Integer dimensionless number
